{"tid":1139244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★若政府就預繳式消費設冷靜期 47%受訪美容業界或結業","createTime":"2019-05-05T06:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T10:54:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":114,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6d74c26d908f55e768c4fd4341166a5caa8396e3","tid":1139244,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"有美容業界團體的調查發現，政府若就預繳式消費冷靜期立法，超過四成七受訪業界表示會考慮結業。<br />\n<br />\n「美容業冷靜期立法關注組」三月至四月問卷訪問1068名業界代表，超過九成人擔心顧客會濫用制度，及造成營運混亂。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦訪問約1100名消費者，六成四人不同意設立「冷靜期」，亦有約七成人擔心立法會令優惠折扣減少，認為現時《商品說明條例》已能處理問題。<br />\n<br />\n關注組認為，應由業界設立自願性冷靜期，及建議政府成立「美容業議會」，處理相關退款及投訴，又指不少退款與服務質素無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5cce6787e603832a43299f39/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5cce6787e603832a43299f39%2F&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=9fd788ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5cce6787e603832a43299f39/</a>"},{"pid":"7194d6759cba6999ded0d1be0db67ab1cbd33163","tid":1139244,"uid":19454,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:11:12.000Z","msg":"結業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf301a769f8a3a121b026aadcb9d17166d07e87","tid":1139244,"uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUod7o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUod7o.png&h=f9f7d04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6AOqd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6AOqd4.png&h=5f413096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji